        &quot;projectId&quot; : 3,
        &quot;parentCommentId&quot; : 2
    }


You are clearly defining `RegisteredUser`, `Project` and `Comment`. Spring doesn&#39;t really know that the property `userId` in your JSON behaves to the `RegisteredUser` object.

&gt; I have tried this
